his history of the peloponnesian war recounts the 5th century bc war between sparta and athens to the year 411 bc. thucydides has been dubbed the father of " scientific history " because of his strict standards of evidence - gathering and analysis of cause and effect without reference to intervention by the gods , as outlined in his introduction to his work .

ancient greece : thucydides , though from this city , tried to be fair to sparta in narrating the peloponnesian war

